channel.title: My old DutchScape source, anyone still got?
channel.description:
Hey guys :)
After a long long brake me and some friends decided to revive my old DutchScape server. Some of the older members maybe remember the server and maybe even downloaded my source. And that, is exactly what i need.
When my old computer crashed and got formatted, my source obviously got deleted, after which i gave up my server.
Now I want to revive it with my old source, but i can't find it anywhere >_< Does anyone still have a (old) version of my DutchScape source?
If so, please post it here, or pm me about it.
Regards,
SirPali, former owner of DutchScape

item.dc:creator: @SirPali SirPali
item.description:
@SirPali wrote:

Hey guys

After a long long brake me and some friends decided to revive my old DutchScape server.
Some of the older members maybe remember the server and maybe even downloaded my source.
And that, is exactly what i need.

When my old computer crashed and got formatted, my source obviously got deleted,
after which i gave up my server.

Now I want to revive it with my old source, but i can’t find it anywhere >_<
Does anyone still have a (old) version of my DutchScape source?

If so, please post it here, or pm me about it.

Regards,

SirPali, former owner of DutchScape
